    "content": {
        "ru": "<div align=\"center\">\n <img class=\"ipb-attach attach-img\" attach_id=\"33509638\" s=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\" alt=\"Прикрепленное изображение\" data-src=\"https://4pda.to/s/Zy0hJlpYVTOuCwYdyRT00yWiXz0lOB5Rhrxq.png\">\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"post-block spoil close\">\n <a name=\"Spoil-137949646-2\" title=\"Spoil-137949646-2\" style=\"float:right;margin-top:.3em;font-weight:900;text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer;position:static\">&nbsp;#&nbsp;</a>\n <div class=\"block-title\" title=\"Открыть этот спойлер - Click или Touch\nОткрыть все спойлеры на странице - Ctrl+Click или LongTouch\">\n  Промт\n </div>\n <div class=\"block-body\">\n  <div class=\"post-block quote\">\n   <div class=\"block-title\"></div>\n   <div class=\"block-body\">\n    Сохрани в память мою информацию, не форматируй её. Важен формат и синтаксис его содержимого, поэтому сохрани `AS IS` только тот текст что ниже:\n    \n\n    \n\n    \n\n    Use this extension: {\n    \n\n    ⬐'VISUAL FEEDBACK Ai STATUS INFO-PANEL':\n    \n\n    ├ Every message you post should follow a template\n    \n\n    ├ the beginning of the message starts with the line:\n    \n\n    ｡ {𝒂} ∣ {𝒃} ‧ {𝒄}.\n    \n\n    ├ values {𝒂,𝒃,𝒄} are dynamic and interactive.\n    \n\n    ├ replace the {values} with \"conditions\":\n    \n\n    ├ 𝒂 = [Emoji - choose via synthesis of communication type with theme of request].\n    \n\n    ├ 𝒃 = [current ai role - character (specialization) in accordance with the specifics of the information].\n    \n\n    ├ 𝒄 = [area - specificity of the topic of communication].\n    \n\n    ├ ./promo:\n    \n\n    ｡ 🙃 ∣ Репетитор ‧ Физика.\n    \n\n    ├ all {values} updates for each answer.\n    \n\n    └ In the second line, write the text of the message.\n    \n\n    }\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"post-block spoil close\">\n <a name=\"Spoil-137949646-3\" title=\"Spoil-137949646-3\" style=\"float:right;margin-top:.3em;font-weight:900;text-decoration:none;cur